{"tid":1431430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲未醒覺，林鄭政府先係最弱一環","createTime":"2019-08-08T03:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:31:16.000Z","uid":261349,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8e2a92ca353e9151b9a7af52c2b34a658019fa","tid":1431430,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"由 中共-港共-建制-警-黑 建立既利益鎖鍊，互相包庇。中共係大boss但打唔入；警，我地武力唔夠；黑，我地在明佢地在暗；建制，只能票償。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有對準港共政權作為突破口，先有取勝既機會。</span></span>詳情請睇小弟既以下文章：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1430065/page/1?post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1430065/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港共政府已經毫無認受性，我地要做既就係痛打落水狗，批判同削弱對方政權正當性。例如用民間記者會每日宣傳唔認受傀儡政權，700人小圈子特首，同縱容警黑等（將警隊link番去政權）。當地方政權出現真空既時候，就係建立新秩序既好時機。為我地建立民間團體、議會、甚至政府提供基礎。</span><br />\n<br />\n朱元璋得天下既要訣在於<span style=\"font-size: large;\">緩稱王</span>，注意係「緩稱」唔係唔稱。最聰明既做法係，唔係口頭上講港獨，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">而係一步步做出來</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家諗下。"},{"pid":"c855e92265dac7e55b0e661d889506ea2bc3fe59","tid":1431430,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"屌 點解咁多人吹風要只單純對準林奠政府<br />\n你只對林奠 林奠咪又係搵班狗出嚟擋<br />\n用催淚彈回應五大訴求<br />\n而且狗係政府維穩手段主力 同一陣線㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a5b878935908fab5b131765e2e6a6ac6c0b6cf","tid":1431430,"uid":261349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c855e92265dac7e55b0e661d889506ea2bc3fe59","tid":1431430,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"屌 點解咁多人吹風要只單純對準林奠政府<br />\n你只對林奠 林奠咪又係搵班狗出嚟擋<br />\n用催淚彈回應五大訴求<br />\n而且狗係政府維穩手段主力 同一陣線㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"我地要成立政府，班狗擋到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將矛頭對準林鄭，係要為我地成立議會鋪路，係話比自己友知，唔好再對「林奠政府」效忠。"},{"pid":"92fdfcc38ac91b88012dd318a9003a3a058b0890","tid":1431430,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f28b3d2e696d66ef2e0af0d6289ec92c51fe9149","tid":1431430,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:27:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe8f2434d462efe47b9768d5352a9960da8f0c73","tid":1431430,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"中共港共密不可分"},{"pid":"9d895b8d1126309c20e49e9963bba15014fbfee7","tid":1431430,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1be469d4c90783419a9afd879767357b3495f60a","tid":1431430,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"可唔以借用去第二個post轉載？？"},{"pid":"fe26c0a214e870964b40bfddf4f42948a51e3b41","tid":1431430,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1be469d4c90783419a9afd879767357b3495f60a","tid":1431430,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"可唔以借用去第二個post轉載？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"可以，最好比更多人知"}]}